            <div class="footer_main--column">
              <strong class="footer_main--column_title">About The Number Ninja</strong>
              <div class="footer_about">
                <p class="footer_about--text">
                  Whether you're looking for someone to manage your business finances, or just a helping hand to make sure you're on the right track, The Number Ninja can help.
